14/* RFC1348. Obsoleted in RFC 1706 - use PTR instead. */
15
16#ifndef RDATA_IN_1_NSAP_PTR_23_C
17#define RDATA_IN_1_NSAP_PTR_23_C
18
19#define RRTYPE_NSAP_PTR_ATTRIBUTES (0)
20
21static inline isc_result_t
22fromtext_in_nsap_ptr(ARGS_FROMTEXT) {
23 isc_token_t token;
24 dns_name_t name;
25 isc_buffer_t buffer;
26
27 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_nsap_ptr);
28 REQUIRE(rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
29
30 UNUSED(type);
31 UNUSED(rdclass);
32 UNUSED(callbacks);
33
34 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_string,
35 false));
36
37 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
38 buffer_fromregion(&buffer, &token.value.as_region);
39 if (origin == NULL)
40 origin = dns_rootname;
41 RETTOK(dns_name_fromtext(&name, &buffer, origin, options, target));
42 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
43}
44
45static inline isc_result_t
46totext_in_nsap_ptr(ARGS_TOTEXT) {
47 isc_region_t region;
48 dns_name_t name;
49 dns_name_t prefix;
50 bool sub;
51
52 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_nsap_ptr);
53 REQUIRE(rdata->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
54 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
55
56 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
57 dns_name_init(&prefix, NULL);
58
59 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &region);
60 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &region);
61
62 sub = name_prefix(&name, tctx->origin, &prefix);
63
64 return (dns_name_totext(&prefix, sub, target));
65}
66
67static inline isc_result_t
68fromwire_in_nsap_ptr(ARGS_FROMWIRE) {
69 dns_name_t name;
70
71 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_nsap_ptr);
72 REQUIRE(rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
73
74 UNUSED(type);
75 UNUSED(rdclass);
76
77 dns_decompress_setmethods(dctx, DNS_COMPRESS_NONE);
78
79 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
80 return (dns_name_fromwire(&name, source, dctx, options, target));
81}
82
83static inline isc_result_t
84towire_in_nsap_ptr(ARGS_TOWIRE) {
85 dns_name_t name;
86 dns_offsets_t offsets;
87 isc_region_t region;
88
89 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_nsap_ptr);
90 REQUIRE(rdata->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
91 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
92
93 dns_compress_setmethods(cctx, DNS_COMPRESS_NONE);
94 dns_name_init(&name, offsets);
95 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &region);
96 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &region);
97
98 return (dns_name_towire(&name, cctx, target));
99}
100
101static inline int
102compare_in_nsap_ptr(ARGS_COMPARE) {
103 dns_name_t name1;
104 dns_name_t name2;
105 isc_region_t region1;
106 isc_region_t region2;
107
108 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == rdata2->type);
109 REQUIRE(rdata1->rdclass == rdata2->rdclass);
110 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == dns_rdatatype_nsap_ptr);
111 REQUIRE(rdata1->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
112 REQUIRE(rdata1->length != 0);
113 REQUIRE(rdata2->length != 0);
114
115 dns_name_init(&name1, NULL);
116 dns_name_init(&name2, NULL);
117
118 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata1, &region1);
119 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata2, &region2);
120
121 dns_name_fromregion(&name1, &region1);
122 dns_name_fromregion(&name2, &region2);
123
124 return (dns_name_rdatacompare(&name1, &name2));
125}
126
127static inline isc_result_t
128fromstruct_in_nsap_ptr(ARGS_FROMSTRUCT) {
129 dns_rdata_in_nsap_ptr_t *nsap_ptr = source;
130 isc_region_t region;
131
132 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_nsap_ptr);
133 REQUIRE(rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
134 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
135 REQUIRE(nsap_ptr->common.rdtype == type);
136 REQUIRE(nsap_ptr->common.rdclass == rdclass);
137
138 UNUSED(type);
139 UNUSED(rdclass);
140
141 dns_name_toregion(&nsap_ptr->owner, &region);
142 return (isc_buffer_copyregion(target, &region));
143}
144
145static inline isc_result_t
146tostruct_in_nsap_ptr(ARGS_TOSTRUCT) {
147 isc_region_t region;
148 dns_rdata_in_nsap_ptr_t *nsap_ptr = target;
149 dns_name_t name;
150
151 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_nsap_ptr);
152 REQUIRE(rdata->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
153 REQUIRE(target != NULL);
154 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
155
156 nsap_ptr->common.rdclass = rdata->rdclass;
157 nsap_ptr->common.rdtype = rdata->type;
158 ISC_LINK_INIT(&nsap_ptr->common, link);
159
160 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
161 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &region);
162 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &region);
163 dns_name_init(&nsap_ptr->owner, NULL);
164 RETERR(name_duporclone(&name, mctx, &nsap_ptr->owner));
165 nsap_ptr->mctx = mctx;
166 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
167}
168
169static inline void
170freestruct_in_nsap_ptr(ARGS_FREESTRUCT) {
171 dns_rdata_in_nsap_ptr_t *nsap_ptr = source;
172
173 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
174 REQUIRE(nsap_ptr->common.rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
175 REQUIRE(nsap_ptr->common.rdtype == dns_rdatatype_nsap_ptr);
176
177 if (nsap_ptr->mctx == NULL)
178 return;
179
180 dns_name_free(&nsap_ptr->owner, nsap_ptr->mctx);
181 nsap_ptr->mctx = NULL;
182}
183
184static inline isc_result_t
185additionaldata_in_nsap_ptr(ARGS_ADDLDATA) {
186 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_nsap_ptr);
187 REQUIRE(rdata->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
188
189 UNUSED(rdata);
190 UNUSED(add);
191 UNUSED(arg);
192
193 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
194}
195
196static inline isc_result_t
197digest_in_nsap_ptr(ARGS_DIGEST) {
198 isc_region_t r;
199 dns_name_t name;
200
201 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_nsap_ptr);
202 REQUIRE(rdata->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
203
204 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &r);
205 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
206 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &r);
207
208 return (dns_name_digest(&name, digest, arg));
209}

211static inline bool
212checkowner_in_nsap_ptr(ARGS_CHECKOWNER) {
213
214 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_nsap_ptr);
215 REQUIRE(rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
216
217 UNUSED(name);
218 UNUSED(type);
219 UNUSED(rdclass);
220 UNUSED(wildcard);
221
222 return (true);
223}

225static inline bool
226checknames_in_nsap_ptr(ARGS_CHECKNAMES) {
227
228 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_nsap_ptr);
229 REQUIRE(rdata->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
230
231 UNUSED(rdata);
232 UNUSED(owner);
233 UNUSED(bad);
234
235 return (true);
236}

238static inline int
239casecompare_in_nsap_ptr(ARGS_COMPARE) {
240 return (compare_in_nsap_ptr(rdata1, rdata2));
241}
